}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== "DX-UH234 VR1.4" is silkscreened on the top of the board for the unit that populated this entry. :"P1M-1109020-02G" is silkscreened on the bottom.
The '''[[NEC]]''' Hub IC is marked with "[[NEC]]", "720114", and "704KF". It is presumed to be a '''μPD720114'''.
The manual specifies... *500mA maximum is provided to each port *The device weighs 1.36oz / [[Weight::38.5g]]. *The dimensions of the device are [[Dimensions::98 mm x 50 mm x 16.5 mm]] *The power adapter (not included) specced for the unit is 5V 2.6A. *The copyright year is 2006 (it's 2005 on the packaging).
